## Project Layout

```
{{ package_name }}/         # main package
config/                     # YAML configuration (auto-merged)
skills/
  custom/                   # your project skills
  community/                # installed from git / skills.sh
docs/
  SKILLS.md                 # skills guide
  EXTENDING.md              # how to add features
```

## Key Commands

```bash
# Agents
cli agents langchain --list              # show configured agent profiles
cli agents langchain -p default --chat   # chat with default agent

# Skills
cli skills list                          # show all skills
cli skills add --skillssh langchain-ai/langchain-skills
cli skills create my-skill               # scaffold a new skill

# Development
just test                                # run tests
just lint                                # lint + validate skills
just fmt                                 # format with ruff
```

